ially in\ncomparison with another recently proposed method by Groen et al (2018). The\nhigh computational efficiency shown by the proposed scheme is also demonstrated\nwith optimisation results for three-dimensional graded microstructures, which\nare not frequently discussed in literature, possibly because of the high\ncomputational cost generated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 06:37:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Dec 2019 01:42:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-18"}
