ee $V({\\mathcal B})_{N,k}({\\mathcal O})$ is finite. We find all the\n${\\mathcal O}_n$-points on these PCF curves $V({\\mathcal B}_{n+1})_{N,k}$ for\n$n=0,1$. When $n=1$ we make extensive use of Skolem's $p$-adic method for\n$p=2$, including its application to Ljunggren's equation $x^2 + 1 =2y^4$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Sep 2019 22:35:44 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 27 Sep 2019 22:52:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-02"}
