tra-faint dwarf galaxies) have donated\nstars to the OHR, while more-massive dwarf galaxies provided the dominant\ncontribution to the IHR.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 01:54:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
