unities are discussed, including the biochemical\nregulation of public goods, more realistic ecological scenarios resembling\nnative environments, cell to cell signalling, and multi-species communities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 08:30:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-26"}
