s has been extensively tested during the selection of new high-energy\npeaked (HSP) blazars recently published in the 3HSP catalog, and has been used\nto search for blazar counterparts of Fermi 3FHL, Fermi 4FGL, AGILE sources, and\nof IceCube astrophysical neutrinos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 25 Sep 2019 12:51:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Oct 2019 13:33:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 25 Nov 2019 13:32:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-11-26"}
